ygData.messageBody:
swim


:)


In actuality I am curious myself. I have raised my faction sufficiently
that I can wander around Freeport, right up until I ran across an NPC high
elf by the name of Lady Faye. She was blue to me so I wasn't afraid of
dying, I just zoned out of Freeport because I was afraid guards would jump
in. Moral of the story is that elves KOS dark elves. Since Feydwer is the
elvish home, it will be problematic at best. Are dark elves KOS to dwarves?
I think it is the dwarven city that the docks are at. I am very interested
in touring crushbone because I believe dark elves are not KOS by those orcs.
